---
import LayoutBare from "../layouts/LayoutBare.astro";
import "../styles/v3-sunset.css";
---

<LayoutBare
  title="Safety Briefing · Jetski Lefkada Rentals"
  description="Safety briefing, equipment, insurance and rules for renting a jetski with Jetski Lefkada Rentals."
>
  <div class="v3 min-h-screen py-32 px-6">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl">
      <a href="/" class="font-mono text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.2em] flex items-center gap-2 mb-12" style="color: var(--v3-flame-500);">
        <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M19 12H5M12 5l-7 7 7 7"/></svg>
        Back
      </a>

      <div class="v3-eyebrow mb-6"><span>Legal</span></div>
      <h1 class="v3-display text-5xl lg:text-7xl mb-4"><em>Safety briefing.</em></h1>
      <p class="font-mono text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.18em] mb-16" style="color: var(--v3-peach-300);">Last updated: April 2026</p>

      <div class="space-y-10 text-base leading-relaxed" style="color: rgba(255,230,212,0.8);">
        <section>
          <h2 class="v3-display text-2xl mb-4" style="color: var(--v3-peach-100);">1. Eligibility & Identification</h2>
          <p>Riders who operate a jetski themselves must be 18 years or older and present a valid government-issued photo ID at pickup. Children are welcome as passengers under adult supervision. Riders under the influence of alcohol, drugs or medication that impairs reaction time will not be permitted to ride.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="v3-display text-2xl mb-4" style="color: var(--v3-peach-100);">2. Pre-Ride Briefing</h2>
          <p>Every rental begins with a 10-minute briefing at Nidri Marina covering throttle and steering controls, lanyard kill-switch use, hand signals, the local route and exclusion zones, and emergency procedures. The briefing is mandatory; you cannot launch without it.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="v3-display text-2xl mb-4" style="color: var(--v3-peach-100);">3. Safety Equipment</h2>
          <ul class="list-none space-y-2">
            <li style="color: var(--v3-peach-100);">✓ <strong>Life jacket (PFD)</strong>: provided and required for every rider and passenger at all times</li>
            <li style="color: var(--v3-peach-100);">✓ <strong>Engine lanyard</strong>: must be attached to the rider's wrist or PFD throughout the ride</li>
            <li style="color: var(--v3-peach-100);">✓ <strong>Whistle and signalling device</strong>: included in the jetski</li>
            <li style="color: var(--v3-peach-100);">✓ <strong>Sun protection</strong>: we recommend bringing sunscreen, sunglasses with strap, and water</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="v3-display text-2xl mb-4" style="color: var(--v3-peach-100);">4. Operating Rules</h2>
          <p>Greek Coast Guard regulations apply at all times: keep a maximum distance of 700 metres from shore, never enter designated swimming zones or buoyed bathing areas, give right of way to swimmers and other vessels, and follow the route discussed in the briefing. Reckless behaviour, jumping wakes near other boats and operating outside the agreed zone may result in immediate termination of the rental without refund.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="v3-display text-2xl mb-4" style="color: var(--v3-peach-100);">5. Weather & Sea Conditions</h2>
          <p>Operations are suspended when wind exceeds Beaufort 5 as required by Greek maritime law. We monitor conditions throughout the day and reserve the right to cut a session short if conditions deteriorate. Weather-grounded bookings are refunded in full or rescheduled at no cost.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="v3-display text-2xl mb-4" style="color: var(--v3-peach-100);">6. Insurance</h2>
          <p>All rentals include third-party liability insurance up to €700,000 per Greek Law 4926/2022. Personal accident insurance is not included; we recommend arranging it separately through your travel insurance. Damage caused by reckless or negligent operation is the renter's responsibility.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="v3-display text-2xl mb-4" style="color: var(--v3-peach-100);">7. Not Comfortable Riding Alone?</h2>
          <p>If you'd rather not drive yourself, we offer guided tours with David, our licensed captain, on board. No license, no minimum age, no experience required — perfect for families with young children, older guests or first-timers. Reach us on <a href="https://wa.me/306955612777" target="_blank" rel="noopener" style="color: var(--v3-flame-500);">WhatsApp</a> for tour details.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="v3-display text-2xl mb-4" style="color: var(--v3-peach-100);">8. Emergency Contacts</h2>
          <p>
            Coast Guard (Greece): <strong>108</strong><br />
            European emergency number: <strong>112</strong><br />
            Jetski Lefkada Rentals: <a href="tel:+306955612777" style="color: var(--v3-flame-500);">+30 695 561 2777</a>
          </p>
        </section>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</LayoutBare>
